  "title": "Infinity Nexus Greenhouse",
  "description": "A simple mod to made a wonderful greenhouse",
  "body": "<blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_40acce98-d36e-4d71-bdf6-7d5986260c10.png\" /></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/rTHRKgm.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><br /></span> <strong>PT/BR</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Infinity Nexus Greenhouser</strong><br />Crie sua estufa do formato que desejar com este Mod vers&aacute;til, intuitivo e f&aacute;cil de usar.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Este Mod funciona com base em receitas, ent&atilde;o nem todas as planta&ccedil;&otilde;es podem estar inclusas.<br /><br /><strong>EN/US</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Infinity Nexus Greenhouse</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Create your greenhouse in any shape you want with this versatile, intuitive and easy-to-use Mod.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This Mod works based on recipes, so not all crops may be included.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://imgur.com/MZLRui3.png\" alt=\"\" /></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>PT/BR</strong></p>\n<p>Um mod simples de gera&ccedil;&atilde;o de colheita de planta&ccedil;&otilde;es simples e f&aacute;cil de usar.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>EN/US</strong></p>\n<p>A simple and easy to use crop generation mod.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://imgur.com/kqk91sc.png\" alt=\"\" /> Custon Recipes: 1.20<br /></strong></p>\n<pre><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">{</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"type\": \"infinity_nexus_greenhouse:greenhouse\",</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"energy\": 100,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"size\": 0,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"plant\": \"minecraft:wheat\", <span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">//Plant</span></span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"properties\": [</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">    {</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">      \"property\": \"age=7\", <span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">//Block property</span></span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">      \"replace\": \"none\" <span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">//minecraft:air</span></span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">    }</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  ],</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"ingredient\": {</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">    \"tag\": \"infinity_nexus_core:up_1\" <span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">//Component Tier</span></span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  },</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  \"outputs\": [</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">    {</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">      \"item\": \"minecraft:wheat\",<br /></span>      <span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\"count\": 1,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">      \"chance\": 1.0</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">    }</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">  ]</span><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">}</span></pre>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">1.21.1</span></strong></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">WIPE</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Compatibilidade:</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Client</strong>&nbsp;</li>\n<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Server</strong></li>\n</ul>",
